                                                <br/>
                                                You can browse our <a style="color:#6C8752" href="http://wheelmap.org/en/blog-2/">Blog</a> and <a style="color:#6C8752" href="http://wheelmap.org/en/faqs/">FAQs</a> if you first want to get to know Wheelmap.org a bit better. Or you learn more about the <a style="color:#6C8752" href="http://wheelmap.org/en/get-engaged/">projects</a> we offer around Wheelmap.org and how you can get involved.<br/>
                                                <br/>
                                                <strong>Keep in touch</strong><br/>
                                                To stay in contact you can subscribe to our monthly <a style="color:#6C8752" href="http://wheelmap.org/en/news-network/newsletter-2/">newsletter</a> and follow us on <a style="color:#6C8752" href="https://www.facebook.com/wheelmap">Facebook</a> and <a style="color:#6C8752" href="https://twitter.com/wheelmap">Twitter</a>. We’re looking forward to hearing your opinion and starting a conversation with you! <br/>
